## Tool Framework

1. Purpose

   - Support development workflow
   - Provide utility scripts
   - Configure development tools

2. Organization

   - .workspace/scripts/: Shared automation (assistant-agnostic)
     - version-bump.sh — SemVer bump (manifest-first)
     - doap-sync.sh — sync doap.json metadata to package.json
   - .workspace/config/: Shared configuration overrides
     - version-bump.conf — optional overrides for version-bump.sh

3. Best Practices
   - Put shared scripts in `.workspace/scripts/`, configs in `.workspace/config/`
   - Keep assistant-specific rules in their respective directories
   - Document tool usage in `.workspace/docs/` and cross-reference from rules
